Think about trans people. If you're a man and you take female hormones, you'll become more feminine and you'll grow boobs because fat gets redistributed but your reproductive organs don't change from male to female. Similarly, if a woman takes testosterone, they won't grow a dick and balls but they'll grow more hair and likely lose fat and gain muscle. Trans people still need to have sexual realignment surgery to change their reproductive organs. Even still, women are born with all the eggs they will ever have.
